  "detailed_description": "Animaddicts is an arcade game.<br><br>The gameplay of Animaddicts is creative and each player can throw a ball at the enemies to transform to a ball. <br>An enemy partially transformed in ball cannot move until it dissolve ( shakes it off ).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878300/extras/88a74f564b257ad8ca83c4eb43c0f9a0.poster.avif?t=1707512879\" width=680 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878300/extras/88a74f564b257ad8ca83c4eb43c0f9a0.webm?t=1707512879\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878300/extras/88a74f564b257ad8ca83c4eb43c0f9a0.mp4?t=1707512879\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features and Content</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Two Characters to choose and play<br></li><li> All level are procedurally and ramdomly generated to add more randomness to each gameplay.<br></li><li> Full Controller Support</li></ul><br><strong>Controller Support</strong><br>This game has Full Controller Support.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1878300/extras/12e59182780d02a9957260ea01f46bef.avif?t=1707512879\" width=600 height=170 /></span>",
